OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA generally
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with the odd brighter
OL,7,Fspells possible, some outbreaks of
OL,8,Fdrizzle possible. Blustery winds
OL,9,Feasing for a time overnight. Cloud and
OL,10,Fpatchy rain arriving from the
OL,11,Fsouthwest by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA cloudy start on Saturday,
OL,14,Fwith thicker cloud pushing
OL,15,Fnortheastwards with outbreaks of
OL,16,Fpatchy rain. Turning increasingly
OL,17,Fwindy as Storm Dave arrives with risk
OL,18,Fof coastal gales developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
